headline: PG&E Applies Enhanced Outage Prediction Models to Ready Crews and Resources Ahead of this Week's Storm
summary: Ahead of the winter storm forecast to deliver strong wind gusts and heavy rain for much of Pacific Gas and Electric Company's (PG&E) service area this week, the company has readied crews and resources to safely and swiftly respond to storm-related outages.
